\f0\b0 \
Jacinth C. Smiley - Executive VP & CFO\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Jeffrey M. Ettinger - Interim CEO & Director\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Jess Blomberg - Director of Investor Relations\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 John F. Ghingo - President & Director\

